00:03:46.189 --> 00:03:50.400
I can learn a lot from them.

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:51.879
My name is Antonelle.

00:03:51.879 --> 00:03:59.939
I live here in Las Vegas, Nevada with my super mom and my troublemaking sister.

00:03:59.939 --> 00:04:03.900
