00:04:16.420 --> 00:04:23.860
I was pretty happy, but Ari was starting to feel the effects of my cancer.

00:04:23.860 --> 00:04:26.060
We just didn't know what it was really.

00:04:26.060 --> 00:04:35.790
One day I was okay and the next day I started feeling bad, you know.

00:04:35.790 --> 00:04:41.259
In my childhood, I played in the usual game.

00:04:41.259 --> 00:04:50.779
I would catch insects, put them in a jar, and then bring them home.

00:04:50.779 --> 00:04:55.699
Then I would get books, such as a criminal procedural code.

00:04:55.699 --> 00:04:58.699
Open them up and start judging one of the books.

00:04:58.699 --> 00:05:04.689
