00:05:04.689 --> 00:05:11.850
I was born into a family where everyone, starting with my grandparents, was either wearing

00:05:11.850 --> 00:05:15.370
an officer's uniform or a judge's robe.

00:05:15.370 --> 00:05:21.709
That's why I had this strong sense of justice.

00:05:21.709 --> 00:05:34.579
But in 1989, my mother was in a tragic car accident, and she got severe burns on her face,

00:05:34.579 --> 00:05:37.860
ends, and body.

00:05:37.860 --> 00:05:47.259
Then my father, I'd seen my mom's condition, decided to leave us.

00:05:47.259 --> 00:05:51.329
Yeah.

00:05:51.329 --> 00:06:01.410
And it was at that moment, I guess, that my world, my ideals, they crumbled.

00:06:01.410 --> 00:06:06.009
I, as a little kid, I always wanted, like, one big happy family.

00:06:06.009 --> 00:06:11.129
