00:06:11.129 --> 00:06:20.399
While I was feeling back then, in New York was just sadness.

00:06:20.399 --> 00:06:26.870
Never really peace.

00:06:26.870 --> 00:06:35.660
Well here in California, we're used to fires.

00:06:35.660 --> 00:06:43.180
But when I got the call to evacuate that morning, I never knew by that evening, the whole

00:06:43.180 --> 00:06:59.100
town of Paradise would be gone.

00:06:59.100 --> 00:07:04.620
Just before the fire, we had the needs of the congregation, where they instructed us

00:07:04.620 --> 00:07:08.060
of what to do, in the case of a disaster.

00:07:08.060 --> 00:07:10.860
I had the truck full of gas.

00:07:10.860 --> 00:07:18.579
