00:07:32.540 --> 00:07:34.860
But they said, obey them.

00:07:34.860 --> 00:07:43.660
So I turned right, though I thought it'd be really bad.

00:07:43.660 --> 00:07:56.579
The smoke got darker and darker, and finally it got black.

00:07:56.579 --> 00:08:04.990
