She always makes me laugh, you know.

00:15:28.740 --> 00:15:33.299
She always helps me have a good time, no matter what.

00:15:33.299 --> 00:15:38.620
Again, friends really help encourage me.

00:15:38.620 --> 00:15:45.580
Proverbs 17-17 says, a true friend shows love at all times, and is a brother who is born

00:15:45.580 --> 00:15:48.779
