I also started to iron clothes for people in their homes, and it looks strange because

00:17:40.339 --> 00:17:45.299
normally where we live, that type of work is done by a woman.

00:17:45.299 --> 00:17:50.380
But for a man to go and iron clothes at someone's home, you don't see that.

00:17:50.380 --> 00:17:54.299
But I didn't want to just sit back with my arms crossed and see what would happen.

00:17:54.299 --> 00:18:01.700
No, I had to put my hands to work to earn a living for my family.

00:18:01.700 --> 00:18:05.059
